<p>Though legislators are running for office and could see some consequences from their votes on road funding, property taxes and other local issues, in the end the counties and cities bear the brunt of the criticism.</p>

<p>â€œWeâ€™ll take the heat for it,â€ said Chadwick. â€œThatâ€™s what we do. Thatâ€™s our job.â€</p>

